{"lemma":"سِمْحاقِ","slug":"سِمْحاقِ","root":"س.م.ح.ق","root_slug":"س-م-ح-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/س-م-ح-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20655"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%90%D9%85%D9%92%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"periosteum"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Uncertain, perhaps representing the Proto-Semitic causative prefix ša- prepended to the root م ح ق (m ḥ q) related to erasure as it is the outer layer of a bone just below the skin and mechanically attrited for bones to be used, however it must be a Southern dialectal term in origin since that prefix is almost everywhere ʾa- or at least ha- in Arabic (while Modern South Arabian preserves this ša-, albeit with the sound /ʃ/)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20655","headword_ar":"سِمْحَاقٌ","root":"smHq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pericranium;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin integument,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above the skull:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Mgh, Msb, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any thin skin resembling that;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) or [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"periosteum"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any bone; i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin that is between the bone and the flesh, above the bone and beneath the flesh;"},{"kind":"text","text":"every bone having what is thus termed: (TA:) [pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samaAHiyqu","text_ar":"سَمَاحِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY","text_ar":"عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"varobi Al$~aApi samaAHiyqu mino $aHomK","text_ar":"ثَرْبِ الشَّاةِ سَمَاحِيقُ مِنْ شَحْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) i. e. (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Upon the fat that covers the stomach and bowels of the sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat is"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thin integument"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin integuments of fat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samaAHiyqu Als~amaA='i","text_ar":"سَمَاحِيقُ السَّمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strata"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin portions of cloud."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"simoHaAqN","text_ar":"سِمْحَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cicatrix which is"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mark of circumcision."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wound by which the head is broken"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aj~apN","text_ar":"شَجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reaching to the thin skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"integument, thus called."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["T","Mgh","Msb","S","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}